WEBVTT

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:15.974
I was praying and the Lord showed me, saying, 'I need you to pray for Italy.'I asked, 'What's going on with Italy, Lord?'He showed me—I had that open vision again—a massive volcano that's about to happen.

00:00:15.975 --> 00:00:21.553
I saw a coastline on the water where there's a massive volcano.

00:00:21.555 --> 00:00:30.205
He told me this is going to happen and there will be signs right before a massive explosion.

00:00:30.206 --> 00:00:41.456
I saw this thing explode huge, and He kept having me pray over the ocean. There's something about the water around Italy.

00:00:41.457 --> 00:00:51.851
I believe the volcano was right there, because Pompeii is right here and there's a massive volcano up here.

00:00:51.852 --> 00:01:01.118
When I was looking over in the spirit realm, I thought it was in this area, but I believe it's probably further out.

00:01:01.119 --> 00:01:06.875
I started looking at where the massive volcanoes in the water are in Italy.

00:01:06.876 --> 00:01:15.901
If you zoom out, I'll show you; one of the largest is way down here.

00:01:15.902 --> 00:01:25.731
Whenever I saw this massive volcano going off out of the water, it caused a massive tsunami wave.

00:01:25.733 --> 00:01:35.954
From the earthquake and this massive volcano, it was like a humongous nuclear bomb went off—it went up out of the water and caused a massive wave.

00:01:35.955 --> 00:01:47.210
The water rushed all over this area, causing a lot of devastation.

00:01:47.211 --> 00:01:55.234
The Lord is showing me it came up out of the water and caused all the air traffic around that area to be completely shut down.

00:01:55.235 --> 00:01:59.304
The Lord showed me it would cost hundreds of thousands of deaths.

00:01:59.305 --> 00:02:16.370
There will be signs, maybe even on the news in Italy, about rumblings around that area, earthquakes, or tremors to warn that something big is going to happen.

00:02:16.371 --> 00:02:34.839
Do not ignore this; it is very serious. If you start having a lot of tremors and you start seeing smoke, take heed.

00:02:34.840 --> 00:02:45.112
Be forewarned; I'm trying to tell you. I was just praying in the spirit, worshiping, and all of a sudden I was shot up.

00:02:45.113 --> 00:02:59.317
I was looking over Italy, and it looked so small because I was so high up.

00:02:59.318 --> 00:03:09.696
I was looking down and all of a sudden I could see a black blanket over the water.

00:03:09.697 --> 00:03:46.715
It was a very thick cloud, as black as molasses, very dark. I could see the black clouds going through all the houses like a smog.

00:03:46.716 --> 00:03:56.876
I could see the rooftops of the homes and the lights on inside.

00:03:56.877 --> 00:04:20.634
The Lord pointed my attention to a massive circle, a humongous portal over Italy near where the volcano was by Pompeii.

00:04:20.635 --> 00:04:41.458
Angels were coming out of this massive portal. It was alive, swirling with clouds, and opening up.

00:04:41.459 --> 00:05:01.345
All of a sudden, thousands of angels started coming out of this massive portal like soldiers, lined up and descending.

00:05:01.346 --> 00:05:44.149
Through the portal, clouds were coming out—humongous, beautiful pink, fluffy, blue, and purple.

00:05:44.150 --> 00:05:53.670
I believe it was Heaven. These angels were descending onto the Earth.

00:05:53.671 --> 00:06:24.371
When they reached the atmosphere, they started to spread out like ants, moving at the speed of light on a mission.

00:06:24.372 --> 00:06:36.186
They all had beautiful robes and gowns on. It was amazing. I'm just sitting here in this chair praying in the spirit, soaking it all in.

00:06:36.187 --> 00:07:28.009
I asked the Lord what that black smog was, and He showed me there is a lot of trafficking and corruption in Italy.

00:07:28.010 --> 00:08:07.025
Those angels were going to homes and waving their hands, telling people to leave, warning them.

00:08:07.026 --> 00:08:37.810
You could sense an urgency on their faces. All of a sudden, the angels stopped.

00:08:37.811 --> 00:09:09.159
I could feel the intercessory prayers from the saints interceding for Italy in the spirit. You could feel the blanket of prayer above the atmosphere.

00:09:09.160 --> 00:09:25.136
All of a sudden, all the angels froze and turned their bodies to look back up to the massive swirling light of the portal.

00:09:25.137 --> 00:09:50.359
They started shooting back up into that portal. Then the Lord took me to another part of the vision.

00:09:50.360 --> 00:10:01.199
He said, 'I want you to focus on the canary.'What is the meaning of a canary in a coal mine?

00:10:01.200 --> 00:10:21.395
Study this out. I saw a yellow canary in a cage. There was gas like a smog coming up out of the ground.

00:10:21.396 --> 00:10:25.677
The canary was swinging in its cage in the spirit realm. It was chirping, but then I looked down at the mist coming up out of the ground.

00:10:25.678 --> 00:10:26.276
When I looked back up, the canary was at the bottom of the cage, lifeless.

00:10:26.277 --> 00:11:39.551
This gas coming up out of the ground in Italy—I don't know if it was from the volcano, but I saw hundreds of thousands of people go home.

00:11:39.552 --> 00:11:44.010
A massive wave was coming. The Lord said to pay attention to the water.

00:11:44.011 --> 00:12:00.538
I saw earthquakes in the water, and He kept pointing me to that in the spirit realm.

00:12:00.539 --> 00:12:21.647
In my spirit eyes, I could see the water in the gulf area, the gulf right there by Pompeii.

00:12:21.648 --> 00:12:32.706
For three weeks now, the Lord has spoken to me about the electric grid in America, telling me to pray over the electric grid.

00:12:32.707 --> 00:13:05.293
This is serious. I saw a cyberattack or a false flag. Power went out in New York and major cities.

00:13:05.294 --> 00:13:16.174
He warned me that I need to pray about this more intently because of what is being planned.

00:13:16.175 --> 00:13:59.912
I saw that when the electric grid went down, it had the opportunity to be down for over three weeks. I saw a calendar with the days going by.

00:13:59.913 --> 00:14:30.198
He showed me a year ago to invest in a generator with three fuel types—propane, gas, and natural gas—and solar power.

00:14:30.199 --> 00:14:47.139
I don't want to preach fear, but I get these intense warnings from the Spirit of God.

00:14:47.140 --> 00:14:57.466
For instance, I was praying over an ice storm once and He told me about Texas being without power.

00:14:57.467 --> 00:15:22.872
I kept seeing no heat and a poisoning of the water. About three years ago, a major arctic front made everything really cold in Texas.

00:15:22.873 --> 00:15:52.363
The grid shut down, pipes burst, and they put out a warning not to drink the water because it had E.

00:15:52.364 --> 00:16:11.605
coli. Before that happened, the Lord warned me to tell friends in Texas they needed cases of water.

00:16:11.606 --> 00:16:30.513
I bought water too because what I was seeing in the spirit was very alarming.

00:16:30.514 --> 00:17:11.389
Even if it doesn't always affect everybody, I want to be quick to obey.

00:17:11.390 --> 00:17:25.750
I saw New York, a major city with big buildings. Pray about the power grid with me.

00:17:25.751 --> 00:19:07.494
I don't want to be a Debbie Downer and coming on here and going wacky all the time, but these are the three things: the canary, Italy, and the electric grid.

00:19:07.495 --> 00:20:10.716
Let's pray. Father, I thank You. We lift up Italy, the volcano, and the earthquakes. You warned us that perilous times would come.

00:20:10.717 --> 00:20:39.232
Shake us and show us what we're supposed to do for our families so we hear You before danger comes. Let us not be led by emotion, but by the Holy Ghost.

00:20:39.233 --> 00:21:00.138
I pray for every person watching this video, that they would learn to yield themselves to the Spirit of God.

00:21:00.139 --> 00:22:52.946
We call for clarity and supernatural giftings to see into the spirit realm.

00:22:52.947 --> 00:23:06.356
We take authority over cyberattacks and false flag events.

00:23:06.357 --> 00:23:12.670
We plead the blood of Jesus over our power grid. We say we will have power.

00:23:12.671 --> 00:24:01.734
Give wisdom to Homeland Security and the computer people to protect us from foreign adversaries.

00:24:01.735 --> 00:24:37.968
Expose all wicked plots. I pray over finances for a hundredfold return.

00:24:37.969 --> 00:25:01.687
I speak blessing over homes—raises, bonuses, and checks in the mail.

00:25:01.688 --> 00:25:55.294
Every need is met and every debt is cancelled. I pray over their health and bodies. We take authority over sickness, cancer, and addictions.

00:25:55.295 --> 00:26:03.201
We call for rain to break drought—the former rain, the latter rain, and even the spiritual rain of the Holy Ghost rain over this nation.

00:26:03.202 --> 00:28:47.115
Bring an outpouring of Your Spirit. We pray for the leaders, from Joe Biden down, that they would have a fear of the Lord to make godly decisions. In Your presence is fullness of joy. We will not fear. Amen.

